    <section id="about" class="about-section">
        <h2>Smile Airlines</h2>
        <p>Welcome to Smile Airlines, where your journey is our priority. We are dedicated to providing world-class
            flight services with a focus on safety, comfort, and convenience. Whether you're traveling for business,
            leisure, or any other reason, Smile ensures a seamless experience from takeoff to landing.</p>

        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="mission">
                <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                <p>To connect people across the globe with safe, reliable, and affordable air travel, while continuously
                    innovating and improving our services to exceed expectations.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="values">
                <h3>Our Values</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Safety:</strong> Your safety is our top priority.</li>
                    <li><strong>Customer Satisfaction:</strong> We strive to ensure every passenger has a pleasant
                        journey.</li>
                    <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> Embracing new technologies for a better travel experience.</li>
                    <li><strong>Sustainability:</strong> Committed to reducing our environmental impact.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="services">
                <h3>Our Services</h3>
                <p>We offer a range of services to meet your needs, including:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>International and domestic flights</li>
                    <li>Comfortable seating and in-flight entertainment</li>
                    <li>Airport lounge access for premium passengers</li>
                    <li>Easy flight booking and ticket management</li>
                    <li>24/7 customer support</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

